  <div class="l-wrap">
    <p>This was my last freelance project, but lot of my "first" moments are associated with it. This was the first project where I had to implement responsive web design, and also this was the first time I tried writing SASS instead of simple CSS.</p>
    <p>Apart from that, I wanted to write server part for the project in a "proper" way: I was learning TDD approach for RoR development with RSpec & Capybara. The website is hosted on Heroku and is using Amason S3 as an asset storage.</p>
